{"tid":2130564,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"方國珊報名參選立法會新界東地區直選","createTime":"2020-07-29T09:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T03:01:15.000Z","uid":336237,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2bf4a3456a95c36caa8d3bde35726105647034dd","tid":2130564,"uid":336237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:33:46.000Z","msg":"【我們報名參選了】<br />\n<br />\n致所有支持我的香港市民： <br />\n<br />\n近日很多市民見我在街頭派發抗疫物資，都追問我會否參選，我方國珊5次參選，屢戰屢敗，但從來沒有放棄將民生議題帶入立法會的決心。因應本港疫情嚴重，我忙於處理防疫事務，故以防疫行先，將私人事件放到一旁，原訂31號才報名，未想到政府會突然放風延遲選舉。<br />\n<br />\n然而，冇人知政府下一步想點做，會唔會突然截龍唔俾報名？或者完全取消，向已報名人士作賠償？我冇政黨冇大水喉，所以唯有被迫改變策略，提前宣布參選。<br />\n<br />\n最後，無論立法會是否延期，都無礙我堅守社區，大家同心抗疫，打贏呢場仗。<br />\n<br />\n方國珊謹啟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0gaS0Z8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0gaS0Z8.png&h=7b79be2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一路走來始終唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2412a8e5c8d09ed17a8dbf421a41a752a0322e","tid":2130564,"uid":303719,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:35:11.000Z","msg":"最強𠝹票機開動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4a57532678dc485a0385ab0516097d6ba83c3a","tid":2130564,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:46:11.000Z","msg":"好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdb8bbd6bd3db60a65cc00e1ec0f4992013b5ed","tid":2130564,"uid":61396,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:48:19.000Z","msg":"大力幫藍絲宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n方 先系最黨愛國"},{"pid":"c9a17c32f997bfda0284a7bcee05539d8814ba5b","tid":2130564,"uid":28277,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:52:35.000Z","msg":"新界東都夠膽來，想輸都唔係咁啊"},{"pid":"04ae12d58c2503d9f02a0a6b47b7428ed0f7321d","tid":2130564,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"其實佢一次都冇選中過佢唔覺得柒嘅咩"},{"pid":"dd124753556318d3a6728e558706cc737a3f7c32","tid":2130564,"uid":335544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04ae12d58c2503d9f02a0a6b47b7428ed0f7321d","tid":2130564,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"其實佢一次都冇選中過佢唔覺得柒嘅咩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:57:26.000Z","msg":"但係佢票數都幾高喎"},{"pid":"847057fd3d6997e505cbd9fdb7bac7e41cd7a484","tid":2130564,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd124753556318d3a6728e558706cc737a3f7c32","tid":2130564,"uid":335544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04ae12d58c2503d9f02a0a6b47b7428ed0f7321d","tid":2130564,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"其實佢一次都冇選中過佢唔覺得柒嘅咩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:57:26.000Z","msg":"但係佢票數都幾高喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:58:04.000Z","msg":"𠝹"},{"pid":"017a593bde01b69310ff5d9c4e719a5d83512966","tid":2130564,"uid":284699,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"dd124753556318d3a6728e558706cc737a3f7c32","tid":2130564,"uid":335544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04ae12d58c2503d9f02a0a6b47b7428ed0f7321d","tid":2130564,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"其實佢一次都冇選中過佢唔覺得柒嘅咩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:57:26.000Z","msg":"但係佢票數都幾高喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"高票但唔當選<br />\n最正係呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe4bed04f0dc273ab65171390